From 38799c21f444895a429fdf4ed9bc0c538498c46e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 12:40:49 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 3/6] dpaa: drivers and board peripherals for LS1046A

- BMan/QMan/FMan: reserved-memory, multi-CPU portals, RSS, PCD
- dtsec: checksum offload (TX+RX), scatter-gather, deferred RX
- New: OH ports, CEETM QoS, FMan chardev, MEMAC MDIO
- GPY115 PHY driver, INA2xx power monitor, QorIQ GPIO fixes
- iicbus: ofw_iicbus devclass fix, pca954x mux support
- UART early printf for QorIQ ns16550
