+ * All rights reserved.
+ *
+ * FMan character device — exposes NCSW PCD API to userspace via ioctls.
+ *
+ * Creates /dev/fm0, /dev/fm0-pcd, /dev/fm0-port-rx*, /dev/fm0-port-oh*
